      </ul>

      <h3>TCEQ</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Written comments accumulating ahead of the August 21 deadline on the EPA minor-source rule</li>
        <li>Any new draft air permits or public-comment notices for gas-fired generation near the eight tracked DFW-area counties</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>County Zoning (DFW + Surrounding Counties)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Fort Worth City Council's August 11 vote: staff's regulatory standards vs. the competing moratorium proposal</li>
